data.description: Location, Location, Location, and character  best describes this lovely stone & hemlock exterior home with way to much to mention.  Formal dining room, chefs delight kitchen, living room with a stone wood insert fireplace, lovely entrance way.  3 spacious bedrooms and 3 full baths.  Finished basement has so much character, with a den with stone fireplace with wood insert, play room or office. Laundry room with so much room and storage that everyone dreams of having. 1 car finished garage in basement, with a nice finished storage room behind it.  1 car detached garage workshop with shed for all your toys. Covered front entrance way, open back deck to enjoy those summer days of grilling and the outdoors.  Call today for your showing.
